eople check out any game they missed out on in that archive,” wrote one user.</p><p> “Hard to argue against any of these in their positions. <em>Rebirth</em> , like <em>Remake</em> , did an insane job with adapting Uematsu&#39;s classic tunes, but also the sheer volume of brand new, outstanding music is just mind-blowing to me. I have no doubt the composers are going to pull out all the stops for the <em>Final Fantasy 7 Remake</em> finale,” added another.</p><p> Last December it was reported that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-planned-dlc-was-scrapped-to-focus-on-final-chapter-of-trilogy-3823714">a planned expansion for <em>Final Fantasy 7: Rebirth</em> was scrapped</a> so developers could focus on the third and final game in the remake project. The game is currently rumoured to be released in 2027 but developers have assured fans <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-7-remake-part-3-playstation-exclusive-xbox-pc-3831750">they won&#39;t need to buy a PlayStation 6</a> (also rumoured to be launching in 2027) to play it.</p><p> In other news, the team behind <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-vi"><em>The Elder Scrolls 6</em></a> have announced a way <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elder-scrolls-6-npc-charity-auction-3838992">for you to be immortalised as an NPC</a> in the long-awaited sequel.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-best-gaming-soundtracks-of-2024-final-fantasy-astro-bot-3839009">These are the best gaming soundtracks of 2024, according to players</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
